unstake.t.sol
├── when the caller is not authorized
│   └── it should revert
└── when the caller is authorized
    ├── given the sablier NFT is not staked
    │   └── it should revert
    └── given the sablier NFT is staked
        ├── it should transfer the sablier NFT to the caller
        ├── it should delete streamOwner
        ├── it should update claim amount
        └── it should emit a {Unstaked} event
